reviewText: THIS DVD COST ME 25.95$ OF MY HARD EARNED CASH AND IT WASN'T WORTH IT!! THE DVD WAS POORLY DONE AND THE SOUND WAS TERRIBLE. 97% OF THE TIME THE FEATURE INSTRUCTOR OF THE DVD HARDLY EVER SHOWNED UP. I HATE I GOT THIS CRAPPY DVD ON THE ART OF JUDO. DON'T BE FOOLED BY THE COOL CASE COVER, IT'S NOT WHAT IT APPEARS TO BE!!!
